    { question: "What exactly is AI phone answering for tradesmen?", answer: "AI phone answering for tradesmen is a 24/7 call handling system designed for anyone working with their hands who can\'t answer the phone while they\'re on a job. Whether you\'re a carpenter measuring up a kitchen, a tiler halfway through a bathroom, or a landscape gardener operating a mini digger, missed calls mean missed jobs. The AI answers every call on the first ring, has a natural conversation with the caller to understand what they need, captures their name, number, location, and job details, then delivers a complete lead summary to your phone within seconds. What makes this different from a basic answering service is the intelligence — the AI understands trade terminology, recognises urgency, and asks follow-up questions relevant to your specific trade. It\'s configured to your business and your services, so callers feel like they\'re speaking to your dedicated receptionist, not a generic call centre." },
